# Köra windowsprogram på linux

- kolla om det går:
	- https://appdb.winehq.org/
- eller bara prova!
- PlayOnLinux 
- Lutris
- CodeWeaver (commercial)

kör med:

    wine program

# ssh client

    ssh [user@]server
	scp fil.txt  [user@]server:~/

nycklar

    ssh-keygen
	ssh-copy-id  [user@]server



# ssh server

kolla config-filen

    /etc/ssh/ssh_config
	
Kolla

    X11Forward
	passwordAuthentification


